#: trndi.api.nightscout3.sparamdesc
msgctxt "trndi.api.nightscout3.sparamdesc"
msgid ""
"** ALPHA DRIVER - Please use \"NightScout\" for daily use! **\n"
"NightScout v3 setup (use FULL access token):\n"
"\n"
"1) Open your NightScout site (e.g., https://your-site).\n"
"2) Go to Admin -> Tokens — or API Secret.\n"
"3) If you use Tokens:\n"
"   - Create a token with at least READ scope.\n"
"   - Copy the FULL access token value exactly as shown.\n"
"4) In Trndi:\n"
"   - Address: enter your NightScout URL\n"
"   - Auth: paste the FULL access token.\n"
"\n"
"Tip: Both \"abc123\" and \"token=abc123\" formats are accepted.\n"
"Note: If you instead use the legacy API Secret, paste your API Secret value as-is.\n"
"Note 2: Your access token should look like: trndi-abc123 (or whatever name you chose)"
msgstr ""
"** ALFADRIVRUTIN - Använd \"NightScout\" för dagligt bruk! **\n"
"NightScout v3 inställning (använd HELA access token):\n"
"\n"
"1) Öppna din  NightScout-sajt (t ex, https://din-sajt).\n"
"2) Gå till Admin -> Tokens — eller API Secret.\n"
"3) Om du använder Tokens:\n"
"   - Skapa ett token med åtminstone \"READ scope\".\n"
"   - Kopiera hela nyckeln, exakt som den visas.\n"
"4) I Trndi:\n"
"   - Adress: ange din NightScout-adress.\n"
"   - Auth: klistra in HELA ditt \"access token\".\n"
"\n"
"Tips: Både \"abc123\" och \"token=abc123\"-formaten accepteras.\n"
"OBS Om du använder en äldre version, med API Secret, klistra in hela hemligheten som den är.\n"
"OBS 2: Din åtkomstnyckel ska se ut som: trndi-abc123 (eller det namn du valt)"

#: trndi.api.nightscout3.sparamdeschtml
msgid "<div style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;\"><div style=\"background: #dc3545; color: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; border: 2px solid #c82333;\">⚠️ ALPHA DRIVER - Please use \"NightScout\" for daily use! ⚠️</div><h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">🌙 NightScout v3 Setup</h2><p style=\"color: #7f8c8d; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 15px;\">(use FULL access token)</p><ol style=\"padding-left: 20px;\"><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">Open your NightScout site (e.g., <code style=\"background: #6495ED; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;\">https://your-site</code>).</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">Go to <strong>Admin → Tokens</strong> — or <strong>API Secret</strong>.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">If you use Tokens:<ul style=\"margin-top: 5px; padding-left: 20px;\"><li>Create a token with at least <strong>READ</strong> scope.</li><li>Copy the <strong>FULL</strong> access token value exactly as shown.</li></ul></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">In Trndi:<ul style=\"margin-top: 5px; padding-left: 20px;\"><li><strong>Address:</strong> enter your NightScout URL</li><li><strong>Auth:</strong> paste the FULL access token.</li></ul></li></ol><div style=\"border-left: 4px solid #0d6efd; padding: 12px; margin-top: 15px; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 0;\"><strong>💡 Tip:</strong> Both <code style=\"background: #6F8FAF; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;\">abc123</code> and <code style=\"background: #6F8FAF; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;\">token=abc123</code> are accepted.</p></div><div style=\"border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 12px; margin-top: 15px; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px 0;\"><strong>📝 Note:</strong> If you instead use the legacy API Secret, paste your API Secret value as-is.</p><p style=\"margin: 0;\"><strong>📝 Note 2:</strong> Your access token should look like: <code style=\"background: #6F8FAF; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;\">trndi-abc123</code> (or whatever name you chose).</p></div></div>"
msgstr "<div style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;\"><div style=\"background: #dc3545; color: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; border: 2px solid #c82333;\">⚠️ ALFADRIVRUTIN- Vänligen välj \"NightScout\" för dagligt bruk! ⚠️</div><h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">🌙 NightScout v3-inställning</h2><p style=\"color: #7f8c8d; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 15px;\">(använd HELA access token:et)</p><ol style=\"padding-left: 20px;\"><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">Öppna din NightScout-sajt (t. ex., <code style=\"background: #6495ED; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;\">https://din-sajt</code>).</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">Gå till <strong>Admin → Tokens</strong> — eller <strong>API Secret</strong>.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">Om du använder Tokens:<ul style=\"margin-top: 5px; padding-left: 20px;\"><li>Skapa ett token med minst <strong>READ</strong> scope.</li><li>Kopiera <strong>HELA</strong> access token:ets värde så som det visas.</li></ul></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">I Trndi:<ul style=\"margin-top: 5px; padding-left: 20px;\"><li><strong>Adress:</strong> ange din NightScout-URL</li><li><strong>Autensiering:</strong> klistra in HELA access token:et.</li></ul></li></ol><div style=\"border-left: 4px solid #0d6efd; padding: 12px; margin-top: 15px; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 0;\"><strong>💡 Tips:</strong> Både <code style=\"background: #6F8FAF; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;\">abc123</code> och <code style=\"background: #6F8FAF; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;\">token=abc123</code> accepteras.</p></div><div style=\"border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 12px; margin-top: 15px; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px 0;\"><strong>📝 OBS:</strong> Om du använder det föråldrade API Secret, klistra in din API Secret så som den visas.</p><p style=\"margin: 0;\"><strong>📝 OBS 2:</strong> Ditt access token ska se ut enligt följande: <code style=\"background: #6F8FAF; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;\">trndi-abc123</code> (eller det namn du valt).</p></div></div>"

